# thoth_mcp_vendor

Creates or updates an MCP vendor allowlist entry used by Thoth enforcement.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_mcp_vendor" "openai" {
  vendor_id     = "openai"
  display_name  = "OpenAI"
  approved      = true
  host_patterns = ["api.openai.com", "*.openai.com"]
  source        = "manual"
  notes         = "Approved by security engineering."
}
```
